												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/hollyhaworth/">Holly Haworth</a></h6>
													Holly Haworth’s essays appear in the <i>New York Times Magazine</i>, <i>Oxford American</i>, <i>Lapham’s Quarterly</i>, <i>Sierra</i>, and at the <i>On Being</i> radio program blog. They have been listed as notable in <i>The Best American Travel Writing</i> and included in <i>The Best American Science and Nature Writing</i>. Her first book, <i>This Resounding World: A Field Guide to Listening</i>, is forthcoming.<span class="Apple-converted-space">																									</div>
